      "seed": 276031741,
      "version": 220,
      "versionNonce": 1037905437,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783440810435,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Does it build? (Build the code)\n2. Run the tests in order of speed\n    - run the fastest tests first, slower tests later.\n        - Run Unit Tests first\n        - Run Unit Integration Tests Next\n        - Run Systems Tests Last\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Does it build? (Build the code)\n2. Run the tests in order of speed\n    - run the fastest tests first, slower tests later.\n        - Run Unit Tests first\n        - Run Unit Integration Tests Next\n        - Run Systems Tests Last\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PehyrcrQ9sodKePtZu11-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1348,
      "y": 607,
      "width": 378.5997314453125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 952674109,
      "version": 113,
      "versionNonce": 1811706173,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783440836789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When you are coding:\n- Write System Tests First\n- Write Unit Integration Tests Second\n- Write Unit tests third.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When you are coding:\n- Write System Tests First\n- Write Unit Integration Tests Second\n- Write Unit tests third.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6AeUf0aZhVQSOb6xfyfBH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1153,
      "y": 820,
      "width": 933.5794677734375,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 847068765,
      "version": 314,
      "versionNonce": 1910026173,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783440908389,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- A system test tests your 'system' (app) from the perspective of the application or user\n     consuming that system. (can you add a show? can you get a list of shows)\n    - System tests MUST be \"isolated\" from any other code you and your team doesn't control.\n        - other services, databases, etc.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- A system test tests your 'system' (app) from the perspective of the application or user\n     consuming that system. (can you add a show? can you get a list of shows)\n    - System tests MUST be \"isolated\" from any other code you and your team doesn't control.\n        - other services, databases, etc.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
